data.description: Well maintained one-story on park-like acreage! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home features a living room with hardwood floors and a cozy wood burning fireplace that is open to the formal dining room. The kitchen has a pantry, eating bar and large nook. Retreat to the primary bedroom, which has a private bath with walk-in shower.  Additional highlights include a generous storage area and a convenient carport/covered patio, ideal for protecting your vehicles and enjoying the outdoors year-round. Enjoy mountain views and the privacy provided by the surrounding trees. This home also comes a refrigerator, washer, and dryer.
